<%# Likes tally: the weighted thumb count (RatingSummary#thumbs). Standalone so
    it can ride in the ratemeta cluster (show page) or next to a browse card's
    byline. Renders nothing when unrated. Expects `summary`. %>
<% if summary&.thumbs %>
  <span class="m-likes"><%= icon(:thumb) %><%= summary.thumbs %></span>
<% end %>
